                        <li>Select 'Pre-Defined Shape' from the menu on the=
 side panel.</li>
                        <li>Select the shape you desire and enter it's dime=
nsions in the unit of your choice.</li>
                        <li>The shape will appear in the center of the map =
as an overlay.</li>
                        <li>It can then be manipulated as per usual.</li>
                    </ol>
